description:
In this video, I'm sharing "SIDE BY SIDE" (Key : C) with you!
This karaoke version of "Side by Side" is great for singing along with the lyrics. It's a fun and easy way to practice your vocals.
If you're looking for a fun and easy way to practice your vocals, then check out this karaoke version of "Side by Side"!

Songwriters: Harry Woods
Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters'  karaoke youtube.
